Anyone who dies in Benares, whether a br창hmin or a prostitute, will become
Siva. When a man sheds tears at the name of Hari, K창li, or R창ma, then he
has no further need of the sandhy창 and other rites. All actions drop away
of themselves. The fruit of action does not touch him.
